OL,7,FHe then revealed to the PM that:
OL,9,F"This is important because there are
OL,10,Fstill some companies - mostly in the
OL,11,Ffinancial area but also highly mobile
OL,12,Fcompanies such as (the pharmaceutical
OL,13,Fgiant) GSK which are investigating the
OL,14,Fpossibility and costs of moving out of
OL,15,Fthe UK. Tax for them is the critical
OL,16,Fissue."
OL,18,FButler on Monday told me: "I am
OL,19,Fwondering what else was sent on (by
OL,20,FMandelson) from me or from anyone else
OL,21,Fin or around No 10.
